reviewText: My 3 year old loves this DVD!

Our kids love all the Nick Jr. DVD's like this one. We do not have cable anymore and I prefer to buy our kids DVD's and Books mostly over toys just because they have so many toys as it is. I always purchase a Nick Jr. DVD a few times a year either for birthdays, Easter or Christmas. They have never not liked one of the DVD's and it was the same case with this one. I would definitely recommend this DVD as well as any of the other Nickelodeon Favorites!
Okay dvd, my kids enjoy the first 2 episodes (Bubble Guppies & Team Umizoomi) and then tend to get bored. Dvd was a good price though.
great collection, except for the Fresh Beat Band episode.

good video , she loves it mix all together , good wild west adventure ,thank you nick , watch for hours .

My girls love all of the Nick Jr. Shows. This DVD contains six Western themed episodes from different shows on Nick Jr.  Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Bubble Guppies - The Cowgirl Parade
2. Team Umizoomi - Shooting Star
3. Dora the Explorer - Pinto, The Pony Express
4. The Fresh Beat Band - Hip Hop Hoedown
5. Go, Diego, Go! - The Great Roadrunner Race
6. The Wonder Pets! - Save the Pony Express/Help the Groundhog
